# Paisa App Development - Walkthrough (Phases 4-8)

This document summarizes the completion of Phases 4 through 8 from the [AI_Accountant_Execution_Prompt.md](file:///Users/sagargoyal/Downloads/AI_Accountant_Execution_Prompt.md), including building structural backend components for the Paisa App.

## Changes Made
- **Database Schema**: 
  - Implemented comprehensive `SQLAlchemy` models ([backend/db/models.py](file:///Users/sagargoyal/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/paisa/backend/db/models.py)) mapping to [transactions](file:///Users/sagargoyal/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/paisa/backend/services/bank_statement.py#82-110), `line_items`, `creditor_dues`, `inventory`, `hsn_master`, and `tally_queue` tables. 
  - Configured a local `SQLite` fallback ([backend/db/database.py](file:///Users/sagargoyal/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/paisa/backend/db/database.py)) to allow immediate local testing.
- **Phase 4 - OCR Fixes**: 
  - Integrated `Cloudflare R2` file storage in [backend/services/storage.py](file:///Users/sagargoyal/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/paisa/backend/services/storage.py).
  - Updated `/api/scan-invoice` endpoint to correctly invoke the LLM extraction logic and upload source images/PDFs to R2.
- **Phase 5 - Tally XML Integration**: 
  - Created Tally `Sales` XML voucher generator in [backend/services/tally_xml.py](file:///Users/sagargoyal/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/paisa/backend/services/tally_xml.py).
  - Built [tally-bridge/bridge.py](file:///Users/sagargoyal/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/paisa/tally-bridge/bridge.py) relay script to constantly poll `/api/pending-tally-posts` endpoints from the backend and send valid XMLs to local Tally Prime.
  - Added FastAPI router for Tally bridge syncing ([backend/routers/tally.py](file:///Users/sagargoyal/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/paisa/backend/routers/tally.py)).
- **Phase 6 - Dashboard**: 
  - Implemented the `/api/dashboard` backend queries over the DB models ([backend/routers/dashboard.py](file:///Users/sagargoyal/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/paisa/backend/routers/dashboard.py)).
  - Scaffolded the frontend structural [Dashboard.jsx](file:///Users/sagargoyal/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/paisa/frontend/src/pages/Dashboard.jsx) tile layout using Vite and Tailwind.
- **Phase 7 - Creditor Tracking + Reminders**:
  - Engineered automated `APScheduler` cron jobs to email payment reminders at 9 AM daily for 7-day overdue invoices in [backend/services/reminder_service.py](file:///Users/sagargoyal/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/paisa/backend/services/reminder_service.py).
- **Phase 8 - Bank Statement Auto-entry**:
  - Implemented `pdfplumber` and `openpyxl`-based bank statement tabular parser inside [backend/services/bank_statement.py](file:///Users/sagargoyal/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/paisa/backend/services/bank_statement.py).
  - Wrote LLM auto-categorization intent logic for grouping bank transactions logically.
  - Exposed `/api/scan-bank` endpoint in [backend/routers/bank.py](file:///Users/sagargoyal/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/paisa/backend/routers/bank.py).

